snippet.title: Goddess Order | Preview
snippet.description:
The past unfolded just as foretold in the "Pages of Fate." 📖

Yet within the final chapter of fate's respun wheel, 
the word "destruction" will be erased. 
Valiant knights start a new journey, guided by your hands. ⚔
